1 under this subdivision to the North Carolina State Treasurer and (ii) require
2 the board of directors of charter schools applying for participation in the Plan
3 to file their applications with the person or entity designated by the North
4 Carolina State Treasurer."
5 SECTION 7.8. G.S. 135-48.30(a) reads as rewritten:
6 "(a) The State Treasurer shall have the following powers and duties:
7 …
8 (20) If delegated by the Board of Trustees under G.S. 135-48.54(b)(2), carry out
9 the powers and duties provided to the Board of Trustees under
10 G.S. 135-48.54(b)(2)."
11
12 PART VIII. EFFECTIVE DATE
13 SECTION 8.1. This act is effective when it becomes law.
